{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f54762e7d0","title":"对栗裕关于舟山群岛南部海面发现美舰的处理报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4ee6a7ca90","index":0,"year":1954,"month":6,"day":2,"articleId":"f54762e7d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"c6c4faabaa","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"菜裕，当时任中国人民解放军副总参谋长。"},{"id":"ebb570baf4","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指票裕1954年6月1日关于舟山群岛南部海面发现美舰的处理情况给刘少奇、朱德并转呈毛泽东的报告。报告说，今晨接华东军区电话称，舟山群岛南部朱家尖岛东南至上下大陈以北之海面，发现敌巡洋舰及驱逐舰共八腰，并有飞机在该海区上空盘旋飞行。似此显系美帝向我军进行挑鲜。当即要华东军区转告该区我军陆海空部队，对当面之敌应严密注意监视，随时报告。如故不向我炮击或轰炸，我军不得向其射击，以免引起冲突。如大陈岛的蒋军乘机向我守岛部队进攻，则应予以坚决回击。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a44c02a2bc","type":"title","text":"对菜裕以关于舟山群岛南部海面发现美舰的处理报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0"},{"id":"c6c4faabaa","type":"paragraph","text":"处理正确，不要先向美军开炮，只取守势，尽量避免冲突","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0"},{"id":"ebb570baf4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0"},{"id":"507f01c4b0","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0"}],"page":{"id":"f555b01a20","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f54762e7d0","start":114,"end":114}}}},"__N_SSG":true}